b(255, 255, 255);box-sizing: border-box;"><div powered-by="xiumi.us" style="box-sizing: border-box;"><div style="box-sizing: border-box;"><div style="padding-right: 10px;padding-left: 10px;font-size: 18px;color: rgb(0, 2, 103);letter-spacing: 1px;box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;">导读</strong></p></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><p style="margin-top: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-indent: 2em;line-height: 1.5em;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);letter-spacing: 0.034em;text-indent: 2em;font-family: mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: var(--articleFontsize);">国常会定调，房地产事关人民群众切身利益，事关经济社会发展大局</span><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);letter-spacing: 0.034em;text-indent: 2em;font-family: mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: var(--articleFontsize);">。2024年1月以来，我国房地产优化政策持续加码，加速落地，但当前销售依旧低迷，拖累经济、地方债务。房地产支持政策应出尽出，应出</span><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);letter-spacing: 0.034em;text-indent: 2em;font-family: mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: var(--articleFontsize);">早出！</span><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);letter-spacing: 0.034em;text-indent: 2em;font-family: mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: var(--articleFontsize);">考虑城镇化进</span><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);letter-spacing: 0.034em;text-indent: 2em;font-family: mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: var(--articleFontsize);">程、改善性需求、城市更新等，房地产还有很大潜力和空间。当前三招可救地产</span><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);letter-spacing: 0.034em;text-indent: 2em;font-family: mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: var(--articleFontsize);">: </span><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);letter-spacing: 0.034em;text-indent: 2em;font-family: mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: var(--articleFontsize);">全面取消限购，持续大幅降息，组建住房保障银行收购开发商库存用于保障房。</span><strong style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);letter-spacing: 0.034em;text-indent: 2em;font-size: var(--articleFontsize);outline: 0px;"></strong></p><p class="channels_iframe_wrp"><mp-common-videosnap class="js_uneditable custom_select_card channels_iframe channels_live_iframe videosnap_live_iframe mp_common_widget" data-type="live" data-headimgurl="https://wx.qlogo.cn/finderhead/Q3auHgzwzM6gibEJdaqnQowZva4PIficn8mjF4jWJysHJDiaJhFUmrrfA/0" data-username="v2_060000231003b20faec8c5ea8c18c0dcca01ef33b07760a0c9dba2cbfd6322e3fff680ebd27d@finder" data-nickname="泽平宏观" data-desc="将在03月27日 15:00 直播" data-livewording="预约" data-intro="【京东金融大咖说】任泽